# Imposter — architecture

## Stack

- **Client:** Vite + React + TypeScript in repo root (`src/`). Tailwind v4 via `@tailwindcss/vite`. **UI:** shadcn/ui in `src/components/ui/` — see rule `imposter-shadcn-ui.mdc`.
- **Realtime game:** Partykit server in `server/` (`server/src/room.ts`, `server/partykit.json`).
- **Discord Activity:** `@discord/embedded-app-sdk` in `src/hooks/useDiscord.ts` when `isDiscordActivity()` (iframe / `frame_id` / Discord UA).
- **Website / PWA:** Same app; when not in Discord, `initWebSession()` in `src/lib/web-session.ts` — localStorage guest id and optional **Supabase anonymous** auth (`VITE_SUPABASE_*`).
- **OAuth token (Discord only):** Cloudflare Worker `workers/discord-oauth-token.ts`; dev uses `vite-plugin-discord-token.ts`.

## Partykit

- Room class: `ImposterRoom` in `server/src/room.ts`. Player keys are **Discord / web user ids** from `JOIN`, not socket ids (`connToUser` maps socket → user).
- Persisted keys: `imposter:stats:v1`, `imposter:round:v1`. Optional `JOIN_VERIFY` in `partykit.json` `vars` checks Discord `@me` with `accessToken` on `JOIN` (Discord Activity only; do not send Supabase JWT as Discord token).

## Client data flow

- `useDiscord()` (name kept for history) returns `auth`, `partyRoomId`, `webMode`, `joinWebPartyRoom`, `createNewWebLobby`, Discord `discordLobbySuffix` / `setDiscordLobbySuffix`, etc.
- `useParty(roomId, userId)` uses `partysocket` + `VITE_PARTYKIT_HOST`.
- `App.tsx` sends `JOIN` on every PartySocket **`open`** (and when identity fields change) so reconnects re-bind `connToUser`. Mid-round new users become **`isSpectator`** until `startGame` or `backToLobby`. Server **45s disconnect grace** before removing a player row. `accessToken` on `JOIN` only for real Discord OAuth when `JOIN_VERIFY` / Activity.

## Adding features

- Shared game types: `src/types/game.ts`. Keep server room types aligned when changing `GameState` / messages.
- Do not commit secrets; `.env` and `.env.deploy` are gitignored. Use `.env.example` / `.env.deploy.example` as templates.
- **Deploy from repo root:** `npm run deploy` reads `.env.deploy` (override with `DEPLOY_ENV_FILE`) and runs Worker (secrets + deploy), Partykit (`JOIN_VERIFY` via `--var`), and Pages (Vite build + `wrangler pages deploy`). Staging template: `docs/STAGING.md`, `.env.deploy.staging.example`.
- **Analytics:** optional Plausible via `VITE_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN`; `src/lib/analytics.ts` + `useGameAnalytics`. **Discussion:** server re-broadcasts state every 25s during discussion for client timer resync.
- **Feedback (R7):** `src/sfx/` — `SfxProvider`, **Sound** toggle in `App.tsx` shell; WAVs in `public/sounds/` (`npm run gen:sfx`); `useSfx()` + `PhaseSfxListener`; vote haptics in `haptics.ts` (skipped when `prefers-reduced-motion`).
- **Room / lobby:** Partykit isolates by `room` string (`useParty`). **Web:** `lobby-{CODE}` from `?room=`, `sessionStorage`, helpers in `src/lib/party-room.ts` + `resolveWebPartyRoomId()` in `web-session.ts`. **Discord Activity:** base instance/channel id, optional `{base}__{CODE}` suffix for split lobbies. Invite/join UI on `Lobby`. **Word packs:** `server/src/word-packs.ts` + `GameState.wordPackId`; client labels `src/data/word-pack-options.ts` (pack ids must match). Optional Partykit **`WORD_PROFANITY_FILTER`** blocks some custom pairs (`SET_NEXT_WORDS`). More ideas: `docs/LAUNCH_PLAN.md` backlog (G\*, X\*).
